8.  Progress is too slow at the beginning of the game

	a.  Give each new player 5 peasants
		Done.

	b.  Replace claim stone mechanism with an instant tower creator.
	    The new player will not have to learn Construction.  Instead,
	    they will simply have to find a suitable location, and then
	    will be able to instantly create a tower there.

	c.  Newbie land (Olympia city?)
		May remain six turns.
		May teleport to any city from newbie land

